          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1706535863423-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Fill the <strong>warmed ciabatta</strong> with the <strong>Cajun-style mayo</strong>, <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>,<strong> sliced tomato</strong> and <strong>crispy Cajun-style king prawns</strong></p><p>Serve with the <strong>chips</strong> and a <strong>lettuce wedge</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle the<strong> lettuce wedge </strong>with a little <strong>olive oil </strong>and the<strong> remaining white wine vinegar</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
